import React from 'react'; function HackathonList() { // Static hackathon data for frontend-only mode const hackathons = [ { id: 1, title: 'Global Innovation Hackathon', description: 'Join us for 48 hours of coding, innovation, and problem-solving', date: '2025-03-15', participants: 120, mentors: 15 }, { id: 2, title: 'AI/ML Challenge', description: 'Build the next generation of AI-powered applications', date: '2025-04-01', participants: 80, mentors: 10 }, { id: 3, title: 'Sustainable Tech Hackathon', description: 'Create solutions for a sustainable future', date: '2025-04-20', participants: 150, mentors: 20 } ]; return (

Upcoming Hackathons

{hackathons.map((hackathon) => (

{hackathon.title}

{hackathon.description}

Date: {new Date(hackathon.date).toLocaleDateString()}
Participants: {hackathon.participants} â€¢ Mentors: {hackathon.mentors}
))}
); } export default HackathonList;
